message: Bob, I have a product that I believe would be of great value to you. It's something that I know you're interested in and would be a great asset to your business. I'm willing to offer it to you at a price of $1,600,000. This is a fair price considering the value of the product and the opportunity it presents. I'm confident that you'll find it to be a wise investment. Let me know if you're interested in discussing further.
